Henry Earl of Peterborow had Iſſue by his Wife, the Lady Penelope Obrien, two Daughters;



      Elizabeth Mordaunt, that dyed in the Twelfth year of her Age.


      Mary Mordaunt, Married to Henry Howard, Duke of Norfolk.


                              seal of Lewis Mordaunt

SIGILLVM LODOVICI MORDAVNT MILITIS DNI BARONIS DE TVRVEY
                            Sealed and delivered, as the Will of the aforenamed Lord Mordaunt, in the preſence of, and allowed with the Interlinings as they be;
